{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act18side", "eventName": "塵影餘音", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "LE-5", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "月光", "storyInfo": "芙蓉勸說車爾尼取消合奏，卻遭拒絕。而彷徨無計的黑鍵發現了一個形跡可疑的人，他似乎與正在夕照區流傳的謠言相關。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "28_g6_whitehome", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clock", "channel": "clk", "loop": "true", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "palysound", "attributes": {"name": "d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你現在感覺怎麼樣，沒問題了嗎？", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒問題......", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒問題的，一定沒問題的。你和我都會沒問題的。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我出去一會兒，你好好在這兒待著。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你才剛好一點，這是要去哪裡？", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#3$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#2$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......去辦事。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#2$2"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#2$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管什麼事，都等到你恢復再說吧。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用擔心我。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "芙蓉也說了，如果醒了，最好休息一段時間，觀察一下情況......", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是急事，很急的事，好嗎？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是我們離音樂會已經沒多長時間了。我覺得現在最重要的還是把身體養好，加緊練習......這也是你的願望啊。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在就別拿這個煩我了，好不好？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煩？", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#4$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#9$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我不是這個意思。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#9$2"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#2$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我確實非去不可，別攔著我了。我會儘快回來的。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#2$2"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#2$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的......不能告訴我要去做什麼嗎？", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#2$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果一切順利的話......你會知道的。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#2$2"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，衣服。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "衣服？", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#3$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "約好今天下午去取的，我沒法陪你去了，你自己去一趟吧。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記得帶大提琴，試穿的時候試著拉一小段，看看會不會有不舒服的地方。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我走了。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 300.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#3$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "clk", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "28_g5_czernyhome", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又是你？", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是我。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我來請求您停辦這次音樂會，至少不要讓黑鍵和白堊在音樂會上合奏了。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說什麼？", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#6$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果讓黑鍵和白堊合奏，夕照區會出大事的！", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按你的說法，我最近身體好轉，是因為黑鍵和白堊引發的所謂“假癒”，但假癒期一過去，我就會變成重症患者，命在旦夕。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，您和他們接觸很多，因此症狀也更明顯。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其他和他們接觸較少的人也會受到影響，如果放任他們合奏，很可能有人死去？", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。雖然原因尚不明確，但讓這兩個人在一起合奏，有很大可能增強他們對周圍的影響。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多大可能？", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "暫時還不知道......", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除了我，還有誰會因此面臨生命危險？", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......夕照區的十多人已經被送去高庭區的醫院了。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高庭區......也就是說，他們已經離開了黑鍵和白堊的影響範圍？", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "應該是這樣的。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白你的意思了。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼......", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不行。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？！", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不奢求您取消整場音樂會，但就算單獨把黑鍵和白堊合奏的曲目撤了也好！或者換人也可以！", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你能證明他們的合奏一定會導致我以外的人受害，我立刻就取消這場音樂會。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但現在不同，連你也無法得知合奏的後果究竟是什麼。我不能僅僅因為虛無縹緲的“擔憂”，就讓整個夕照區的努力和希望付諸東流。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "整個夕照區的努力和希望？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我理解您對這次音樂會的重視程度，但是......", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不理解。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你真的理解，就不會輕飄飄地說出那個“但是”。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很遺憾，我不能僅憑你的一面之詞改動音樂會的安排。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "車爾尼先生，請您直接告訴我，這次音樂會和感染者的生命相比，究竟重要在什麼地方？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你什麼意思？", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#6$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes":